eya_def_tools.data_models.eya_def.EyaDefDocument
IEC 61400-15-2 EYA DEF top-level data model.
Attributes: uri (Optional[Url]): URI of the EYA DEF JSON document, which should have the field name '$id' in the JSON document. Default is None. schema_uri (Url): URI of the EYA DEF JSON Schema, which should have the field name '$schema' in the JSON document. It is assumed to be the latest published version if not included. Default is https://raw.githubusercontent.com/IEC-61400-15/eya_def/blob/main/iec_61400-15-2_eya_def.schema.json. uuid (Optional[UUID]): UUID of the EYA DEF JSON document. Default is None. title (str): Title of the energy yield assessment (EYA) report. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the energy yield assessment (EYA) report. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the energy yield assessment (EYA) report. Default is None. project_name (str): Name of the project under assessment. project_country (Alpha2CountryCode(StrEnum)): The ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 two-letter code of the country where the project under assessment is located. document_id (Optional[str]): The ID of the report document; not including the version when 'document_version' is used. This will typically follow the convention of the document management system of the issuing organisation(s). Default is None. document_version (Optional[str]): Version of the report document, also known as revision. As with the 'document_id', this will typically follow the document versioning convention of the document management system of the issuing organisation(s). Default is None. issue_date (date): Report issue date in the ISO 8601 standard format for a calendar date, i.e. YYYY-MM-DD. contributors (list[ReportContributor]): List of report contributors (e.g. author and verifier) issuing_organisations (list[Organisation]): The organisation(s) issuing the report (e.g. consultant). receiving_organisations (Optional[list[Organisation]]): The organisation(s) receiving the report (e.g. client), if relevant. Default is None. contract_reference (Optional[str]): Reference to contract between the issuing and receiving organisations that governs the energy yield assessment (EYA) report document, if relevant. Default is None. confidentiality_classification (Optional[str]): Confidentiality classification of the report document, if relevant. Default is None. epsg_srid (int): EPSG Spatial Reference System Identifier (SRID) for the Coordinate Reference System (CRS) used for all spatial data (e.g. turbine locations) in the EYA DEF JSON document. All location coordinates must be reported in the same CRS, which must be one that has an EPSG code. If different CRSs are used the data must be converted to be consistent with the EPSG code specified here. measurement_stations (Annotated[Optional[list[dict[str, Any]]], IEATask43WraDataModel]): List of measurement station metadata JSON document(s) according to the IEA Task 43 WRA Data Model, for all station datasets used in the EYA, if any. Default is None. reference_wind_farms (Optional[list[ReferenceWindFarm]]): List of reference operational wind farms used in the EYA. Default is None. reference_meteorological_datasets (Optional[list[ReferenceMeteorologicalDataset]]): List of reference meteorological datasets used in the EYA. Default is None. wind_resource_assessments (list[WindResourceAssessment]): List of wind resource assessments, including results, at the measurement station locations. turbine_models (Annotated[Optional[list[dict[str, Any]]], IEC61400x16PowerCurveDataModel]): List of wind turbine model specifications. Default is None. scenarios (Optional[list[Scenario]]): List of energy yield assessment scenarios. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.general_metadata.Organisation
Issuing or receiving organisation of an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Entity name of the organisation. abbreviation (Optional[str]): Abbreviated name of the organisation. Default is None. address (Optional[str]): Address of the organisation. Default is None. contact_name (Optional[str]): Name(s) of contact person(s) in the organisation. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.general_metadata.ReportContributor
Contributor to an energy yield assessment.
Attributes: name (str): Name of the contributor. email_address (Optional[EmailStr]): Email address of the contributor. Default is None. contributor_type (ReportContributorType(StrEnum)): Type of contributor. contribution_comments (Optional[str]): Comments to clarify contribution. Default is None. completion_date (Optional[date]): Contribution completion date (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_met_data.ReferenceMeteorologicalDataset
Metadata for a reference meteorological dataset.
The schema describes a dataset at a single horizontal spatial location. Separate data model instances need to be used to describe data at different location from the same source dataset (e.g. different grid cells from a reanalysis dataset).
Attributes: id (str): Unique ID for the reference meteorological dataset within the EYA DEF document. description (str): Description of the meteorological dataset. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the meteorological dataset. Default is None. location (Location): The horizontal spatial location of the meteorological data.

eya_def_tools.data_models.reference_wind_farm.ReferenceWindFarm
Reference wind farm.
Attributes: id (str): Unique ID for the reference wind farm within the EYA DEF document. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the reference wind farm. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the reference wind farm. Default is None. wind_farm_configuration (WindFarmConfiguration): The configuration data for the reference wind farm. datasets (list[ReferenceWindFarmDataset]): Metadata for the operational dataset.

eya_def_tools.data_models.scenario.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: id (Optional[str]): Optional unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the scenario. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the scenario. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (float): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (TurbineWindResourceAssessment): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. energy_assessment (EnergyAssessment): Energy assessment details and results, including gross energy, plant performance, net energy and uncertainties.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.WindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the measurement location(s).
Attributes: wind_resource_assessment_id (str): Unique ID of the wind resource assessment within the EYA DEF document. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the wind resource assessment. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the wind resource assessment. Default is None. results (WindResourceResults): Results of the wind resource assessment at the measurement location(s).
